  <brief_title>Six Month Clinical Research Study for Patients With Moderate or Severe Dry Eye Syndrome</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Allergan</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Allergan</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A six-month clinical research trial to evaluate the effectiveness of an investigational
      medication for the treatment of dry eye syndrome in patients that have been diagnosed with
      moderate to severe dry eye syndrome, an autoimmune disorder AND/OR females 65 years of age or
      older.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
